      "seed": 420002,
      "version": 396,
      "versionNonce": 1733253201,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776370028120,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Run and Debug (launch.json)\n  -> support/hooks.js [dotenv]\n  -> step_definitions/auth.steps.js [Given]\n  -> helpers/api.js [createClient + getAuthParams]\n  -> helpers/api.js [HTTP call /members/me or /boards/:id]\n  -> step_definitions/auth.steps.js [Then status]\n  -> helpers/assertions.js [assertMemberId/assertBoardId]\n\nBreakpoints-chave:\n- Given: validar env + this.api = createClient()\n- When: antes de await this.api...\n- API: antes de http.get(...)\n- Then: antes de assert.strictEqual(...)\n- Assertions: inicio de assertMemberId/assertBoardId",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Run and Debug (launch.json)\n  -> support/hooks.js [dotenv]\n  -> step_definitions/auth.steps.js [Given]\n  -> helpers/api.js [createClient + getAuthParams]\n  -> helpers/api.js [HTTP call /members/me or /boards/:id]\n  -> step_definitions/auth.steps.js [Then status]\n  -> helpers/assertions.js [assertMemberId/assertBoardId]\n\nBreakpoints-chave:\n- Given: validar env + this.api = createClient()\n- When: antes de await this.api...\n- API: antes de http.get(...)\n- Then: antes de assert.strictEqual(...)\n- Assertions: inicio de assertMemberId/assertBoardId",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
